creator: Sara Teasdale
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 24 recordings of Red Maples by Sara Teasdale. This was the Weekly Poetry project for June 1, 2014. Read in English by Andrew Coleman; Assaf Koss; Arup Sen; Amanda Vickery; David Lawrence; Ernst Pattynama; Ezwa; fshort; Garth Burton; JemmaBlythe; Jason Mills; Jannie Meisberger; Julia Niedermaier; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Malcolm Fisher; Phil Schempf; Ruth Golding; ravenotation; SkyAlbatross; Seamus Dobbin; Shakira Searle; Salma97 and Teresa Bauman. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (12MB)
